@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us - News&Reviews App";
}

<style>
    h2, h3 {
        color: #9be52a;
        padding: 5px;
    }

    p {
        color: cyan;
        font-family: "Calibri", sans-serif;
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    li {
        color: white;
        font-family: "Calibri", sans-serif;
        font-size: 18px;
    }
</style>

<div class="container">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Welcome to News&Reviews App! We are a game-related website dedicated to bringing you the latest news and in-depth reviews about different games across various platforms. Our inspiration comes from sites like ign.com, aiming to provide you with a rich gaming experience.
    </p>

    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Users can create and manage their profiles to stay connected with the gaming community.</li>
        <li>Get detailed information about game news and reviews, including platforms, genres, publishers, and release dates.</li>
        <li>Utilize powerful filtering and searching tools to easily find specific game reviews and news.</li>
        <li>Enjoy a user-friendly and responsive design that ensures seamless usage across devices.</li>
        <li>Have full control over your user data, ensuring your privacy and security.</li>
        <li>Engage with fellow gamers through our interactive forum, fostering a vibrant community.</li>
        <li>Discover your next gaming adventure through our unique quiz functionality, helping you find the perfect game genre to play.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Contributing</h3>
    <p>
        At the moment, our community contributions are closed. However, we greatly appreciate your interest in contributing to enhance our platform!
    </p>

    <h3>License</h3>
